# Helper Functions

### Left Height

```java
private int leftHeight(TreeNode node){

    int height = 0;

    while(node != null){
        height++;
        node = node.left;
    }

    return height;
}
```

---

### Right Height

```java
private int rightHeight(TreeNode node){

    int height = 0;

    while(node != null){
        height++;
        node = node.right;
    }

    return height;
}
```

